'''[[Velanaria]]n boxing''' was a form of martial arts that involved the use of four [[Limb/Legends|arms]]. There was a crosscut version of the art, which [[Rodo]] was familiar with. The bouncer had known a being that could perform some of the style, however, he informed [[Nova Stihl]] that the techniques didn't translate that well to a being with only two arms. During their brief friendship aboard the [[DS-1 Orbital Battle Station/Legends|Death Star]], Rodo taught the [[Stormtrooper/Legends|stormtrooper]] a technique during a sparring match.

